text: Pervomaysk () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Pervomaysky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 355 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 85 km from Krasnaya Gorka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Pervomaysk, Republic of Bashkortostan
